      "voiceId": "logan-paul",
      "voiceName": "Logan Paul",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "This Sunday, the auction for the Holy Grail of Pok\u00e9mon closes. The current bid is at $6.3M, already making it a two-time Guinness world record setting collectible.  By this time next week, someone will own this franchise-defining piece of history We\u2019ll be live streaming it all LIVE on my YouTube channel as we\u2019re breaking open a $1,400,000 1st Edition & Legendary Collection box of Pok\u00e9mon cards. I am GASSED \ud83d\udd25 9pm EST, this Sunday on my YT channel. See you there",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@loganpaul/video/7605625226159869198",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-11T15:11:14+00:00",
